items.PortalKey_MJ_D01.description = <msg key="server.items.PortalKey.description"/>\n\n<i>A strange shard that holds knowledge of the location of <color is="#e81634">Baal's Kingdom.</color> This particular one leads to its entrance - <color is="#e81634">The Main Gates.</color> Only here can one find the shard that will allow one to proceed further.</i>\n\nAdded by MAJOR DUNGEONS.

