items.PortalKey_MJ_D02.description =  <msg key="server.items.PortalKey.description"/>\n\n<i>A strange shard that holds knowledge of the location of <color is="#e81634">Baal's Kingdom.</color> This particular one leads to <color is="#e81634">The Blood Castle</color>, the lair of an ancient dynasty of vampires sworn to protect their leader, <color is="#e81634">Baal</color>.</i>\n\nAdded by MAJOR DUNGEONS.

